/*

Purpose:			


Return Value:	has to change to return actual time but for testing will just make it 2 hrs from start of jobs	


Date		Who		Reason
26 January 2007	cnwer1	Initial creation - PAR#xxxx

*/
vars
	time : TimeStamp;
